        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>National Historical Publications and Records Commission Reauthorization Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill reauthorizes the National Historical Publications and Records Commission for FY2020-FY2025 and adds the Council of State Archivists as a member of the commission.</p>]]></text>
